id="post-2583" class="post-2583 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-energy category-environment category-transportation tag-bus tag-shelter tag-sustainable"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2010/09/16/sustainable-bus-shelter/" title="Permalink to Sustainable Bus Shelter" rel="bookmark">Sustainable Bus Shelter</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2010/09/16 11:07 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2010/09/16/sustainable-bus-shelter/" title="Sustainable Bus Shelter" rel="bookmark">2010/09/16 11:07 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p>Waiting for the bus is not the most exciting thing to do in the world, but it is a very necessary one. (And let&#8217;s face it waiting for a bus and reading a book is better than starring at a license plate in front of you during a traffic jam.) Designer Tiffany Roddis has come up with a bus shelter that is better than most and is also good for the environment.<br
/> <img
src="http://i0.wp.com/s3images.coroflot.com/user_files/individual_files/343120_P6BrkQXBzHVuBltSbZghEsQrw.jpg?w=520" alt="Bus shelter" data-recalc-dims="1" /></p><blockquote><p>The stylish new eco friendly bus stop will attract new tourists and new custom to lower pollution from existing car owners. The frustration of late buses and complicated timetables can now be reassured by the new colour coded main head-stream. It’s easy-read route finder can accommodate everyone, comforting users that they can arrive to work, school or general destinations on-time by guaranteed GPS signals.</p></blockquote><p><a
href="http://www.coroflot.com/public/individual_file.asp?from_url=true&#038;individual_id=343120&#038;portfolio_id=3996904&#038;">Here&#8217;s Tiffany&#8217;s project page.</a></p><div
class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-1111807-2583-538344bb917a8' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=1111807&amp;post_id=2583&amp;origin=www.thingsaregood.com&amp;obj_id=1111807-2583-538344bb917a8' data-name='like-post-frame-1111807-2583-538344bb917a8'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div
